CustomField.description: Membership stops using the values in the three "Receipt and Acknowledgement Version Name" fields on this date, so receipt/acknowledgement copy isn't used past the point in which it would be dated (such as not keeping up with current news events). Membership Communications staff, who write the copy for the various receipt/acknowledgement versions, set this date.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Last date these versions will be used.
CustomField.label: Rcpt or Ack Version Expiration Date
